annotations:
  artifacthub.io/category: skip-prediction
  artifacthub.io/changes: |
    - kind: added
      description: One-command local setup (scripts/local-quickstart.sh + examples/postgis-dev.yaml) and a docs/quickstart.md with a troubleshooting table.
    - kind: added
      description: Preflight validation of JWT/email secret length and known placeholders, plus a FITPUB_DATABASE_URL JDBC check, so misconfig fails at install time with a clear message.
    - kind: changed
      description: development-values.yaml now uses localhost:8080 so port-forwarded links work out of the box.
